issue.body:
Goals
------

* Connect to `Msys2 OpenSSH Server` correctly.

ENV Preparation
------

1. Install `Msys2` to `C:/msys64` according to https://www.msys2.org/
2. Uninstall `Win32-OpenSSH Client & Server`
3. Turn off Windows firewall (Or add a rule that allows `TCP/22` traffic to access Windows)
4. Setting up `Msys2 SSHd` according to https://www.msys2.org/wiki/Setting-up-SSHd/
    - Use the script to set up `Msys2 SSHd` as the Windows service

Database and authentication

Update hrrr.py

1. Remove wind_uv_at_height because it is a bad interpolation of data from different heights.

2. Add wind_velocity_direction_at_altitude because that is more useful in calculations.
Add fringe_deg to the max_lat and max_lon.

Enable 10m 80m above ground search.

This enables searching the grib messages for the 10m and 80m above ground in addition to isobaric pressure levels.
Flip atan2(u, v) to atan2(v, u)
Cache xarray.Datasets when calculating wind speed and direction.
Make adjustment to agree with prevailing winds.
Adjust the wind direction in degrees so it matches a wind rose.
Convert longitude degrees east to degrees west.
Use bilinear interpolation to find U and V.
Refactor math to make it more clear.
Updates to make code more clear.
Add option for orographic model to the configuration file
added food good/bad SFX + checked volumes on puzzle food

review.body:
@nSedrickm I like the fact that patternfly is getting applied to upstream. But TBH I don't like it being applied for just one component and leaving it at that.

If we are introducing patternfly here its going to break some things in the dashboard like the search bar in table, and some minor UI elements, some parts of the form. Also this makes somethings in the dashboard being bigger while somethings being smaller and that causes inconsistency between the UI elements. It looked to me like a minorly broken dashboard. 

And I was checking the size of the bundle generated and it was around 43M with patternfly there. But the interesting this is it was 40M without the patternfly. That should not be ideal.

Some broken elements.
